40:46.458 --> 40:49.875
<i>- ♪ The best that you can do ♪
- ♪ The best that you can do ♪</i>

40:50.000 --> 40:52.000
<i>♪ The best that you can do ♪</i>

40:52.625 --> 40:53.666
<i>♪ Is fall in love ♪</i>

