- <i>♪ The best that you can do ♪</i>
- <i>♪ The best that you can do ♪</i>

41:17.666 --> 41:20.041
<i>♪ The best that you can do ♪</i>

41:20.166 --> 41:21.666
<i>♪ Is fall in love ♪</i>

41:21.791 --> 41:25.416
<i>♪ When you get caught
between the moon and New York City ♪</i>

41:47.000 --> 41:48.250
You should run now.

41:52.541 --> 41:53.666
Was that the Chimera?

41:58.458 --> 42:00.166
<i>Poseidon's never helped me before.</i>

42:03.166 --> 42:04.583
<i>He wasn't gonna start now.</i>
